release.name: v0.0.16: PathMapper constructors
release.body: `PathMapper` now provides three constructor methods, `PathMapper.file_mapper`, `PathMapper.dir_mapper_shallow`, and `PathMapper.dir_mapper_deep`. This split of functionality simplifies the internal code logic and also makes the API more explicit.

issue.title: How to convert all .nii images into 2d jpg images from a directory?

Greeting, i am unable to convert my all nii images into 2d images. I have more than 1000 nii images that I have to convert in 2d images. But through given instruction I only able to convert one nii to jpg at a time.
Please someone help or share the script to convert all nii images that are in a directory.
Thanks
